nodes.text: A male Yuuzhan Vong shaper with a lisp was on Yuuzhan'tar in 28 ABY. At one time, he was approached by Hooley Krekk, who wished to know what the shaping cortexs were. The shaper filled Krekk in, unknowingly giving Nom Anor, who was posing as Krekk, the last bits of evidence to prove that the eighth cortex was fake.
